verbose_text: Furthermore, Jak and Fgfr inhibitors promote primed and naive pluripotency signatures in Erk5 +/+ or Erk5 -/- mESCs (XREF_FIG H), confirming that Erk5 does not modulate transcriptional responses to these key pathways.
